    {
      "id": "0124278b-674f-4758-b9d5-13d701b621cf",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Academic achievements is a hall-mark of a high quality academic institution and the performance of students in the firsat year is usally a good indicator of student success later down the line. ",
