    {
      "id": "129650a2-5031-491f-a107-a23776d1c97e",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors use Semi-Supervised learning to classify students in an Indonesian University based on their performance - Medium/High. Authors use sample of 140 students and 27 features. The approach starts with the use of clustering (k-Means) followed by classification (Naive Bayes).  Model performance published indicate very high performances.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "129650a2-5031-491f-a107-a23776d1c97e",
        "parent": {
